          "contents": "# TODO - Write the take_break() function for the break reminders\n\n\n\n# TODO - Write the check_todo() function for the to-do list reminders\n\n\n\n# TODO - Replace the repeated blocks by calling your new functions\nprint(\"🧠 Don't forget to take a short break.\")\nprint(\"⏱️ Stretch, get water, and rest your eyes.\")\n\nprint(\"📋 What's next on your to-do list?\")\nprint(\"✅ Pick one task and get started.\")\n\nprint(\"🧠 Don't forget to take a short break.\")\nprint(\"⏱️ Stretch, get water, and rest your eyes.\")\n\nprint(\"📋 What's next on your to-do list?\")\nprint(\"✅ Pick one task and get started.\")\n",
